{"word":"προμνάομαι","slug":"προμνάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προμνάομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to woo</i> or <i>court for</i> another, <el>ἡ προμνησαμένη</el> = <a href='S:προμνήστρια'><el>προμνήστρια</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>generally, <i>to solicit</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>προμνᾶταί τί μοι γνώμα</el> my mind <i>forebodeth</i> somewhat, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}